 ly SELECTED artists pay a fixed USD 50 selection fee (USD 40 early-bird) t
 o participate in the exhibition\; most selected artists pay this fee and d
 o not receive a cash grant. Money-back guarantee on the selection fee unti
 l the official exhibition opening day. Up to 10 artworks per artist\; max 
 2 may be selected. Deadline 9 June 2026.\n\nOrganisation: Biafarin\nLocati
 on: Online (Canadian organisation\; worldwide submissions and online exhib
 ition)\nAward: Cash grants per artist: Major Grant CAD 500 (1 artist)\; Me
 rit Grant CAD 250 each (4 artists\, total CAD 1\,000 pool)\; Recognition G
 rant CAD 100 each (10 artists\, total CAD 1\,000 pool). NOTE: submission i
 s free\, but SELECTED ARTISTS PAY a USD 50 selection fee (USD 40 early bir
 d) to participate in the exhibition. Money-back guarantee on the selection
