  Photography)
DESCRIPTION:Women Photograph + Leica Project Grants 2026 awards three grant
 s of USD 10\,000 each to support documentary photography projects. ELIGIBI
 LITY: open to women\, nonbinary\, transgender\, and intersex documentary p
 hotographers of any nationality\; no membership required\; no restrictions
  on camera equipment or career stage. Funding covers hard costs of reporti
 ng\, photographers' creative fees\, and any other expenses that support th
 e production of new or in-progress still photography projects. Not intende
 d for books\, exhibitions\, or workshops. Grantees retain full work owners
 hip. One submission per applicant\; applications in English (Google Transl
 ate acceptable)\; any use of generative AI must be disclosed. Applications
  opened 20 May 2026\; deadline 30 June 2026 at 11:59 PM ET. Apply at https
 ://app.picter.com/contests/bad7ea97-7b0d-4a9c-9e85-38e73529d62b/start.\n\n
 Organisation: Women Photograph (supported by Leica USA)\nLocation: Remote 
 (international)\nAward: Three grants of USD 10\,000 each (USD 30\,000 tota
 l). No application fee.\nDuration: Project-based (new or in-progress photo
 graphy projects).\n\nMore: https://app.picter.com/contests/bad7ea97-7b0d-4
 a9c-9e85-38e73529d62b/start
URL:https://app.picter.com/contests/bad7ea97-7b0d-4a9c-9e85-38e73529d62b/st
 art
