UID:lee-ufan-arles-art-environment-prize-2026@artificialnouveau.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260701T070201Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260731
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260801
SUMMARY:Deadline: Lee Ufan Arles: Prix Art & Environnement 2026 (Residency 
 + Exhibition Prize)
DESCRIPTION:The Prix Art & Environnement (4th edition)\, awarded by Lee Ufa
 n Arles and Maison Guerlain\, supports an artist working at the intersecti
 on of art and the natural environment. The prize winner receives a funded 
 6–8 week production residency in Arles in early 2027\, including product
 ion space\, accommodation\, and mentorship from Lee Ufan Arles staff\, cul
 minating in a solo summer 2027 exhibition. ELIGIBILITY: open to all artist
 s of any discipline and nationality\, with no age or degree requirements\;
  candidates must demonstrate at least one solo exhibition and one or more 
 group exhibitions. DEADLINE: 31 July 2026. APPLY via the Google Form linke
 d from the Lee Ufan Arles website.\n\nOrganisation: Lee Ufan Arles and Mai
 son Guerlain\nLocation: Arles\, France (residency and exhibition)\nAward: 
 Funded residency (production space + accommodation) in Arles. No cash priz
 e amount specified. No application fee.\nDuration: 6–8 weeks residency i
 n early 2027\, followed by a solo summer 2027 exhibition\n\nMore: https://
 en.leeufan-arles.org/evenements/art-environment-prize
URL:https://en.leeufan-arles.org/evenements/art-environment-prize
LOCATION:Arles\, France (residency and exhibition)
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
